This document describes the Language Server Protocol (LSP) integration in the Elemental orchestrator, providing code intelligence features (autocompletion, hover, diagnostics, go-to-definition) for the Monaco editor.

## Architecture Overview

The LSP integration uses a server-side approach where language servers run on the orchestrator-server and communicate with the browser-based Monaco editor via WebSocket.

