- \`captureEditorContent\` â€” leave as-is
- \`suppressChangeRef\` in LspMonacoEditor â€” leave as-is (still useful for model switch suppression)
- Tab replacement logic â€” leave as-is
- LSP notification logic â€” leave as-is

